{"tid":384474,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"切生果有泡係咪化學野？","createTime":"2017-09-02T10:32:14.000Z","updateTime":"2017-09-02T15:46:57.000Z","uid":126099,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"0db6cde366a7b51fc224dfcce9bbda6700959a66","tid":384474,"uid":126099,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-02T10:32:14.000Z","msg":"有個食家朋友平時上佢屋企成日食好西<br />\n介紹左檔生果佢經常幫襯，早兩日買左一堆生果<br />\n由於平時係有師傅切埋菠蘿既，但因為果日去既時候都幾夜，師傅收左工，我自己都識切就照買。<br />\n<br />\n但今日切菠蘿果陣 每次切落去把刀都有d泡<br />\n好似洗手液果d咁，但唔係好多<br />\n<br />\n咁多位連登巴打知唔知係正常？定打左針？<br />\n<br />\n利申其他生果好正常，Google過無資料"},{"pid":"30c3fc23773c40728d9f6fd1aa21fd06171e7b00","tid":384474,"uid":126099,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-02T11:12:45.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"75a50ed134d50c1220d581b47d0c67ed7a431b55","tid":384474,"uid":38191,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-02T11:16:41.000Z","msg":"可以等死<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/offtopic.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"abef2fcb1edc43970e270afc81410db6417be90f","tid":384474,"uid":838,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-02T11:18:07.000Z","msg":"把刀未過乾淨水<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4b4398e6960fc9385780429b6828e37d716a2ed3","tid":384474,"uid":60651,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-02T11:31:53.000Z","msg":"下世小心啲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"79091b251ec71cf1f93223cf4598948ad5a1b633","tid":384474,"uid":126099,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-02T12:23:28.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>把刀未過乾淨水<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n肯定沖左，每次切完都有洗"},{"pid":"efc663e1e0da934a0ea27f5f518bf79d01dcf63a","tid":384474,"uid":126099,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-02T12:23:44.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>下世小心啲